+    /// Regression for BUG_AUDIT_2026_04_30_CORE.md #88: previously
+    /// the TTL gate was `hop_ttl > 0 && hop_count >= hop_ttl`,
+    /// short-circuiting to "always forward" when `hop_ttl == 0`.
